    • wrapOpt

      public static String wrapOpt​(String str, char wrapWith)
      Wraps an option string with a string if that one is missing from the start or end of the given option string. A new string will not be created if the given option string is already wrapped.
      Parameters:
      str - the option string to be wrapped, may be null
      wrapWith - the char that will wrap the given string
      Returns:
      the wrapped option string
